and risk.SystemId = advrxxchangedbeans.SystemId
where risk.cmmcontainer in ('Policy')
and concat(advrxxchangedbeans.adddt,advrxxchangedbeans.addtm)>='$$m_strtdt' 
and concat(advrxxchangedbeans.adddt,advrxxchangedbeans.addtm) <='$$m_Enddt'
